491
00:32:04.291 --> 00:32:07.595
if you can't beat them.

492
00:32:08.629 --> 00:32:10.631
<i>be</i> them.

493
00:32:10.698 --> 00:32:12.533
[angelic music]

494
00:32:12.600 --> 00:32:14.335
<i>Let me show you around.</i>

495
00:32:14.402 --> 00:32:16.437
