I was gonna have equality.

527
00:34:16.991 --> 00:34:20.761
I was gonna have
to create it myself.

528
00:34:20.828 --> 00:34:23.931
So that's when the three
of us. a bioengineer.

529
00:34:23.998 --> 00:34:26.433
